Metasoma: 1.33 × as long as wide; T 2 with submedial pits with fan of striae anterolaterally; 1.5 × as wide as long; T 3 - T 6 without any distinct sculpture; single setae present laterally on T 3 - T 6 ; length and width of T 1 -T 6 being: 0.06 : 0.26 ; 0.21 : 0.32 ; 0.03 : 0.29 ; 0.02 : 0.22 ; 0.02 : 0.13 ; 0.02 : 0.06 respectively (
